OL,3,CScout hut destroyed in devastating fire
OL,5,FA scout group in Berkshire have been
OL,6,Fleft devastated after a fire destroyed
OL,7,Ftheir hut.
OL,9,FThe blaze at 1st Mortimer Cubs and
OL,10,FScouts group last Wednesday (April 22)
OL,11,Fcaused the roof to collapse into the
OL,12,Fbuilding.
OL,14,FNo-one was injured by the fire which
OL,15,Fis believed to be accidental.
OL,17,F"There is no evidence of vandalism or
OL,18,Fmalicious intent," the group said in a
OL,19,FFacebook post.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
