OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1777313467
OL,3,CScout hut destroyed in devastating fire
OL,5,FThe post continued: "In our 116 years
OL,6,Fof Scouting in Mortimer, we have faced
OL,7,Fmany challenges, and each time we have
OL,8,Ffound a way through.
OL,10,F"However, we believe this may be the
OL,11,Fgreatest challenge in our history.
OL,13,F"While the loss of our home is deeply
OL,14,Ffelt, the response from our community
OL,15,Fhas been nothing short of incredible.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
