FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1777313467
OL,3,CScout hut destroyed in devastating fire
OL,5,F"In true Scouting spirit, we have
OL,6,Falready received many offers of
OL,7,Ftemporary accommodation for our
OL,8,FBeavers, Cubs, Scouts and Rover
OL,9,FScouts, for which we are hugely
OL,10,Fgrateful.
OL,12,F"We are absolutely determined to keep
OL,13,FScouting in Mortimer alive for the
OL,14,Fnext 100 years and beyond.
OL,16,F"To help us do this, we are asking for
OL,17,Fdonations, no matter how big or small.
OL,18,FYour support will help us cover the
OL,19,Fimmediate additional costs of keeping
OL,20,Fall sections running, and support us
OL,21,Fin rebuilding our much-loved home.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
