FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1777313467
OL,3,CScout hut destroyed in devastating fire
OL,5,F"Together, we can not only recover
OL,6,Ffrom this devastating event, but
OL,7,Fcreate something even stronger, an
OL,8,Fimproved and enhanced home for future
OL,9,Fgenerations, and a lasting asset for
OL,10,Four whole community.
OL,12,F"If you would like to support us,
OL,13,Fplease visit our GoFundMe page."
